1932;;Evenings for Sale;;American;;Stuart Walker;;Herbert Marshall, Sari Maritza;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evenings_for_Sale;;Impoverished Count von Dopenthal (Marshall) plans to commit suicide and spends his last night at a costume ball. There he meets lovely Lela Fischer (Maritza) and falls in love with her. A chance meeting with his former butler, brings a job offer as a gigolo.